Rating: 3
I made this cookie at work and was pleased with the yield. At first I was afraid I wouldn't get enough from the recipe, but even portioning these cookies with a "small" (in relation to my "regular" scoops) produced very big cookies. They spread much more than you'd guess. Drizzling them with chocolate made them very visually appealing. Nice flavor - make sure you like the quality of the peanuts as it will be the primary flavor - even with the chocolate.

